videos.headline: Juwan Gary somehow gets the and-1 to fall
videos.description: Juwan Gary gets hit on the way up and knocks down the basket for the Alabama and-1.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Juwan Gary somehow gets the and-1 to fall) 2022/01/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Juwan Gary runs the break with huge slam
videos.description: Juwan Gary throws  down the big  dunk in transition for Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Juwan Gary runs the break with huge slam) 2022/01/08 ESHEET

videos.headline: Trevon Brazile skies for big alley-oop slam

videos.headline: Missouri punctuates upset win over Bama on Gordon's slam
videos.description: DaJuan Gordon picks off a pass on defense and takes it all the way for a dunk to put the finishing touches on Missouri's win over No. 15 Alabama.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Missouri punctuates upset win over Bama on Gordon's slam) 2022/01/08 ESHEET
